info.description:
Apex Bench has a simple, elegant look that is at home in any setting. It can also be linked end to end in continuous runs.
  • Standalone benches in nominal 6 foot lengths

  • Add-on sections available for continuous runs

  • Aluminum frame with a durable powdercoat finish

  • FSC 100% Jatoba hardwood slats (FSC License Code: FSC-C004453)

  • Surface mount

  • High recycled content; fully recyclable
info.name: Apex Bench
